{
  "stem": "25651.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Fredy Hirsch was quite an extraordinary man, a tremendous gymnast, and a sort of-- outgoing, laughter-- personality.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Laughter was around him always.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything was a joke.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He took a view of the camp the first role call in the morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we all called out our names so that he would get acquainted with us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were there about three days or four days already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there must have been about five-- perhaps a hundred-- perhaps more-- all in this one-- one-- hut.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were all six, seven-- that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I said, [NON-ENGLISH] Honigwachs, and he said, oh, one of the royal family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he immediately explained-- to my chagrin-- he immediately explained that every-- that we were six brothers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And every one of the brothers was [NON-ENGLISH] in Novy Jicin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you look at [NON-ENGLISH] Honigwachs-- and I was then six.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He will one day be [NON-ENGLISH], Novy Jicin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I never actually-- [LAUGHS] --got to that, because the war intervened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What I remember then was about two or three days later, we played something which we called a wide game, which was the red army against the blue army.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we all had bands on our sleeves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And since I was the smallest, I was in-- I was a runner to the general staff of the blue army.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the general of the blue army was Fredy Hirsch, you see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we all went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The general staff went to one side of a valley.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's very beautiful countryside, you know, meadows in the middle-- sort of a gentle valley with a brook running through it, and forests-- small forests-- to either side so that there would be cover.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You'll see who could attack from the forest.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
